node.text: I don’t know what motherhood is going to be like. Everyone has such different experiences and perspectives—I’ve learned to just trust the process and take each day at time. Watch as I share with my @kerastase_official family part of my pregnancy experience. #KerastaseGenesis #Kerastase #KerastaseClub #partnership

node.text: A lot of hard working people in this country feel disillusioned and disconnected from politics. They have every right to. For far too long they have not been represented or protected by those in power. I believe @berniesanders is our chance to change that.
